video_title: If You Find It Hard To Set Boundaries | Dr Julie
transcript:
if you find it hard to set boundaries
with other people here's one thing that
might be holding you back
you see it as all or nothing either you
put everyone else first or you put you
first and putting yourself first feels
too selfish to bear so your default is
to put them first but having healthy
boundaries doesn't mean you have to stop
caring about other people's needs just
means you have to start treating your
own as equal to theirs
